      <title>耶伦呼吁加强金融稳定工作和深思熟虑的监管</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-call-more-financial-stability-work-thoughtful-regulation-2024-09-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长耶伦将呼吁继续努力确保金融体系的韧性，包括推行深思熟虑的监管并反击那些想要降低银行资本要求的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-call-more-financial-stability-work-thoughtful-regulation-2024-09-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:34:48 GMT</pubDate>
